OGC
Initial of /Original Geometry Computation/

For segment based geometry learning,
it will keep updating.


Currently containing: 

API 'point'   => point.cpp   point.h
API 'segment' => segment.cpp segment.h
API 'polygon' => polygon.cpp polygon.h
usage flow    => main.cpp
auto make     => Makefile


To make all:
  ./make

To make library only:
  ./make lib

To run:
  ./run

To clean:
  ./make clean

To make unit test:
  ./make gtest

To run unit test:
  ./unittest

To clean unit test:
  ./make gtclean
